-- Hong Kong Billionaire Lee May Buy Shaw's TVB Stake, Apple Daily Reports
-- B y   W i n g - G a r   C h e n g
-- 2010-09-25T02:18:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-25/hong-kong-billionaire-lee-may-buy-shaw-s-tvb-stake-apple-daily-reports.html
Hong Kong Billionaire Lee Shau-Kee
may pay about HK$9 billion for a majority stake in Television
Broadcasts Ltd., Apple Daily reported, without saying where it
obtained the information.  Lee will acquire the stakes held by TVB Chairman Sir Run
Run Shaw and Shaw Brothers (Hong Kong) Ltd., the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wing-Gar Cheng in Beijing at 
 wgcheng@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stanley James at 
 sjames8@bloomberg.net  